  <brief_title>TBTC Study 23: Treatment of HIV-Related Tuberculosis Using a Rifabutin-Based Regimen</brief_title>
  <official_title>TBTC Study 23: Treatment of HIV-Related Tuberculosis Using a Rifabutin-Based Regimen</official_title>
