  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Primary objective:

      To determine the rate of confirmed treatment failure and relapse with an intermittent
      rifabutin-based regimen for the treatment of isoniazid and rifamycin-susceptible HIV-related
      tuberculosis (TB).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
